        <Parent_String>modern Russian fine arts styles and movements [300111618], modern Russian styles and movements [300021391], modern European regional styles and movements [300021175], modern European styles and movements [300021424], European [300020656], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
